              },
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma-ray yield was",
                "normalized to the differential cross section of",
                "Del Bianco et al. in the deuteron energy range Ed=2.9",
                "to 4.2 MeV. The normalization factor was then used to",
                "determine the absolute yield below Ed=2.9 Mev."
              ]
            }
          ],
